# TI Seminar Scheduler - Project Standards

## Project Overview
TI Seminar Scheduler is a web application for managing lecturer teaching schedules.
Built with Next.js 14+ (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and Convex database.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 14+ with App Router
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS with CSS variables for theming
- **Database**: Convex (real-time, serverless)
- **UI Components**: Custom components following Atomic Design pattern
- **CSV Parsing**: PapaParse

